<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-in-out;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ECC71, #145A32);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 5px solid #1D8348;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 180px;
            animation: popIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content h1 {
            color: #2ECC71;
            font-size: 26px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 25px;
            background-color: #2ECC71;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.3);
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #27AE60;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .social-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #444;
        }
        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .social-icons img {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .social-icons img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.2);
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        @keyframes popIn {
            from { transform: scale(0.8); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px;
            }
            .button {
                padding: 12px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Gradific Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. You can reset your password by clicking the link below:</p>
            <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button">Reset My Password</a>
            <p>If you didn’t request this change, you can safely ignore this email—your account is still secure.</p>
            <p>For your security, this link will expire in 1 hour. If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Gradific Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="social-section">Stay connected with us! Follow us on:</div>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="https://x.com/gradific"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733579.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/gradific/"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2111/2111463.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/gradific"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733547.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
            </div>
            <p>&copy; {{year}} Gradific. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
